00:48:52,505 --> 00:48:53,585
so he took the car.

602
00:48:54,464 --> 00:48:55,464
Once he arrived,

603
00:48:55,545 --> 00:48:57,984
he carelessly got out of the car.

604
00:48:58,065 --> 00:48:59,705
According to Saen,

605
00:48:59,785 --> 00:49:02,025
he has evidence proving
it was an accident.

606
00:49:04,464 --> 00:49:06,185
