609
00:49:12,384 --> 00:49:14,825
One minute later, Saen's car drove past

610
00:49:14,904 --> 00:49:16,825
in the same direction.

611
00:49:17,825 --> 00:49:19,545
Fifteen minutes later,

612
00:49:19,625 --> 00:49:22,545
