They say,

679
00:54:00,145 --> 00:54:03,904
older people perceive
The Little Prince differently

680
00:54:03,984 --> 00:54:05,904
than children.

681
00:54:07,185 --> 00:54:08,864
You should read it again.

682
00:54:09,585 --> 00:54:12,625
You might understand
and perceive it differently this time.

683
00:54:15,185 --> 00:54:16,145
Dad.

684
00:54:40,944 --> 00:54:42,785
-No.
-Be careful!

685
00:54:55,785 --> 00:54:56,705
Saen.

686
00:54:59,545 --> 00:55:00,384
Na.

687
00:55:10,585 --> 00:55:12,265
It's really you, Saen.

688
00:55:43,305 --> 00:55:44,384
Mrs. Na.

689
00:55:45,105 --> 00:55:45,944
Mrs. Na.

690
00:55:49,464 --> 00:55:51,025
Mrs. Na!

691
00:55:51,785 --> 00:55:53,065
No.

692
00:56:05,145 --> 00:56:06,025
Let's move.

693
00:56:07,904 --> 00:56:09,025
What's going on?

694
00:56:09,105 --> 00:56:11,225
-What?
-Are you hurt anywhere?

695
00:56:13,265 --> 00:56:15,904
How careless of you.
Do you have a death wish?

696
00:56:15,984 --> 00:56:16,825
Jan.

697
00:56:16,904 --> 00:56:18,504
It's…

698
00:56:18,585 --> 00:56:19,745
-Well…
-Saen.

699
00:56:20,345 --> 00:56:23,105
Do you see other men
as your husband again?

700
00:56:23,185 --> 00:56:25,345
-When will you stop being crazy?
-Jan.

701
00:56:25,424 --> 00:56:26,864
Saen is my husband.

702
00:56:26,944 --> 00:56:28,424
-Can you hear me? Mine.
-Jan.

703
00:56:28,504 --> 00:56:30,625
-He's mine.
-Stop or I'll call the police.

704
00:56:30,705 --> 00:56:31,825
-Get off her.
-Stay out.

705
00:56:33,864 --> 00:56:35,585
Make sure she takes her medicine.

706
00:56:35,665 --> 00:56:37,424
She shouldn't talk to anyone's man.

707
00:56:37,504 --> 00:56:38,825
Weren't you the one

708
00:56:38,904 --> 00:56:40,265
who left Saen for Sib?

709
00:56:40,745 --> 00:56:41,625
What a lunatic.

710
00:56:41,705 --> 00:56:42,745
Gosh.

711
00:56:42,825 --> 00:56:44,185
-Move.
-My goodness.

712
00:56:44,265 --> 00:56:45,265
What the…

713
00:56:45,345 --> 00:56:46,504
My goodness.

714
00:56:49,665 --> 00:56:50,625
Let's go inside.

715
00:56:50,705 --> 00:56:51,545
Okay.

716
00:56:55,265 --> 00:56:56,504
-Gosh.
-What?

717
00:56:56,585 --> 00:56:57,785
I feel sorry for Na.

718
00:56:58,585 --> 00:56:59,984
And what is Jan's problem?

719
00:57:00,065 --> 00:57:02,825
