733
00:57:30,705 --> 00:57:33,464
might have a really strong heart.

734
00:57:34,864 --> 00:57:37,185
And people who seem strong

735
00:57:37,265 --> 00:57:41,185
might have wept more tears
than we could imagine.

736
00:58:24,984 --> 00:58:26,145
Keep an eye on him

737
00:58:26,625 --> 00:58:28,345
and keep me updated.

738
00:58:42,464 --> 00:58:45,185
Weren't you the one who left Saen for Sib?

739
00:58:47,464 --> 00:58:48,625
Na.

740
00:58:50,904 --> 00:58:51,984
Yes, Grandma.

741
00:58:54,464 --> 00:58:55,345
I…

742
00:58:56,944 --> 00:59:00,904
I don't know how much time I have left.

743
00:59:02,145 --> 00:59:05,305
I'm worried about you.

744
00:59:06,585 --> 00:59:09,265
You are a woman.

745
00:59:10,825 --> 00:59:12,225
