Why did you say that after I kissed you?

1125
01:29:47,664 --> 01:29:49,145
It's how I felt.

1126
01:29:52,265 --> 01:29:53,545
I don't believe you.

1127
01:29:54,385 --> 01:29:56,265
Who sent you here?

1128
01:29:56,905 --> 01:29:57,945
Tell me.

1129
01:29:59,025 --> 01:29:59,985
Tell me now.

1130
01:30:11,265 --> 01:30:14,305
This is Nut. His first name is Peeranut.
He's 27 years old.

1131
01:30:14,385 --> 01:30:16,185
His mom is Matana. His dog is Kuenchai.

1132
01:30:16,265 --> 01:30:17,105
Tofu!

1133
01:30:17,784 --> 01:30:19,465
That's plenty of information.

1134
01:30:20,505 --> 01:30:21,784
You say you don't know him.

1135
01:30:21,864 --> 01:30:24,545
I'm Tofu, your teddy bear.

1136
01:30:26,305 --> 01:30:28,425
I never thought you would be such a liar.

1137
01:30:28,505 --> 01:30:30,225
Excuse me.

1138
01:30:31,545 --> 01:30:32,585
You seem lonely,

1139
01:30:32,664 --> 01:30:34,305
like you have no friends to talk to.

1140
01:30:35,065 --> 01:30:38,385
Right. Nut told me you live alone.

1141
01:30:39,065 --> 01:30:40,425
Your husband doesn't visit.

1142
01:30:42,065 --> 01:30:43,065
Is the room okay?

1143
01:30:43,145 --> 01:30:44,185
Yes.

1144
01:30:44,265 --> 01:30:46,025
I was Nut's teddy bear.

1145
01:30:46,824 --> 01:30:48,905
Why did I become your look-alike?

1146
01:30:52,025 --> 01:30:53,585
What are you doing, Dad?

